    <item>
      <title>随着Boj Rate越来越大的债券损失，日本债券损失在全球</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/japan-confronts-biggest-bond-loss-globally-as-boj-rate-hikes-upend-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本银行在过去一年中，日本银行对息税率上涨的枢纽之后，投资者正在重新考虑日本主权债券的策略，这引发了全球债务市场的最大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/japan-confronts-biggest-bond-loss-globally-as-boj-rate-hikes-upend-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 23:35:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当交易者权衡特朗普威胁俄罗斯处罚时，石油稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果无法达到与乌克兰的停火，投资者权衡了唐纳德·特朗普总统对俄罗斯原油的新惩罚威胁的影响，那么石油就稳定了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 23:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管机构在主要澳大利亚交易所的旗帜合规性缺陷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/regulators-flag-serious-compliance-issues-at-australian-exchange</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚的市场监管机构和中央银行确定了与贸易解决方案有关的交换运营商ASX Ltd.的严重问题，他们说需要立即采取行动才能解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/regulators-flag-serious-compliance-issues-at-australian-exchange</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 22:37:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票下跌加深，债券随着贸易商的脱发：市场包裹而上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/us-stock-futures-tumble-ahead-of-new-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）之前，股票在亚洲早期下跌，推出了新的关税。由于担心全球贸易战的经济影响，Gold受到避风港的需求刺激了新的记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/us-stock-futures-tumble-ahead-of-new-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 22:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金升起以记录，因为贸易战门关注推动避风港需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/gold-rises-to-record-as-trade-war-concerns-drive-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金以新的纪录开始了一周，这是唐纳德·特朗普总统预期的最新关税弹力，这加剧了对全球贸易战争的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/gold-rises-to-record-as-trade-war-concerns-drive-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 22:13:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
